      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? You've found it! This beauty runs like a dream and has been kept in wonderful shape over the years. It's super clean, comfy, and ready for all your upcoming road trips or daily commutes. I\u2019ve absolutely enjoyed every mile in this car, and I\u2019m sure you will too. Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to show it to you and get you behind the wheel!",
