    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior retains a beautiful factory shine, though a discerning eye will notice minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather seats are supple with only light wear on the driver's entry bolster. All electronic features, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a consistent service history. It recently underwent a full inspection, resulting in fresh fluids and a new set of brake pads. It starts up quietly, idles smoothly, and provides a tight, responsive feel through the steering wheel. This is a solid, honest car that has many years of dependable service left to offer.",
      "price": 34500.0,
